Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:03:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Once there was a man who had it all,\NPirate King Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,His final words spurred people\Nto take to the seas in droves:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've left everything\Nthis world's got to offer {\i1}there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.41,0:03:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And so men set sail for the Grand Line\Nin pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, the world is in the midst\Nof the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Live as you please, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In the flow of time, as a result of\Nvarious circumstances and strong spirits,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,people come to question the world they live in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The day we meet will come at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The judicial island Enies Lobby is the front door
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:04:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that leads to the World Government,\Na huge organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that they've caused it to fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,neither the Navy nor pirates\Nwill leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say that the Straw Hats\Nare now known all around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.76,0:04:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And so is this wanted poster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji! You're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this incredible?!\NIt's the spitting image of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He pulled one crazy stunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look! It's an article on Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like he toppled the Tower of Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.27,0:04:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,His bounty is going to skyrocket after that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Enies Lobby is famous\Nfor Water Seven's sea train.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't that far from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.34,0:04:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be a twist of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.78,0:05:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,For them to be within range...\NWhat a pitiable, unfortunate crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.57,0:05:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Get ready to set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We're about to get busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Teach!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back three days before the\Nworld was shocked and amazed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,by the Straw Hat Pirates' wanted posters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There was an event that\Noccurred on a certain island.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Banaro Island in the Grand Line.
