Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.24,0:05:56.21,Title Card - Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur0.6\fad(1973,1973)\4a&HFF&}Blackbeard's Darkness Attacks Ace
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ace! Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.40,0:06:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me "Commander" after all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That word is meant to be\Nreserved for people you respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mock me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you must be Fire Fist Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.53,0:06:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's me. Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... you've already become\Na great captain in your own right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Captain Marshall D. Teach\Nof the Blackbeard Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.51,0:06:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, Ace! I haven't seen you in ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's the deal?\NHow'd you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach, let's cut the idle talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.46,0:06:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know the rules, having lived\Nthrough twice as much as others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But let me say something first!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say, Ace?\NWhy don't you join my crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Seize the world with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already planned out how\NI'm going to rise up in power!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Whitebeard's reign is over!\NI'll become the next Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,For starters, I'm gonna kill\NStraw Hat Luffy, who is in Water Seven,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,as a gift to the Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy? What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You know him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Another reason I can't let you go free!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And naturally, there is no way I'm going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.86,0:07:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...join your crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:07:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,One of your men could use a lesson in manners!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Flame Commandment!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Pillar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Auger, Burgess! Keep outta this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't stand a chance\Nagainst that man. Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,--Sorry!\N--Fire Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,--Captain!\N--Aw, that burns!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.47,0:08:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot, hot, hot, hot, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot, hot, hot, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, hot, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Hot, hot, hot, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, men! Give me some space!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.99,0:10:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it, Ace. You're burning\Nto kill me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no surprise. Murdering a\Ncrewmate is a grievous crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that I killed the\N4th division commander Thatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have a choice! He got his hands on\Nthe Devil Fruit that I had my sights set on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.24,0:10:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship's rule dictated that whoever\Nfound the fruit could eat it, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I memorized what every fruit\Nin the book looked like,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so I knew it was the one I'd been\Nlooking for the second I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The only reason I spent all those\Ndecades on Whitebeard's ship
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,was because I figured that was\Nthe most likely place to find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I woulda given up if fortune\Nhadn't smiled down on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but that fruit fell into my friend's hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:11:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So then you killed Thatch and stole it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's how the ball bounces.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This ability chose me, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It has made me the most\Npowerful person out there, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! It's rare, even for a Logia type.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace, isn't your body made out of fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine is darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! It's the same black smoke from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Those pirates are still in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They're still going at it?\NIf they destroy any more of our village...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep away from them!\NOur only option is to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:12:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Darkness...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Commander Ace. You can't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.86,0:12:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's said that this is the most\Nevil power in Devil Fruit history.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Logia Devil Fruit, Dark-Dark Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've become a man made of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a taste of just how powerful it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and try.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.03,0:12:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The captain is about to cut loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't hurry away from here,\Nwe'll get caught in the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.59,0:12:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand right back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The darkness gushing from his body\Nis crawling across the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.76,0:13:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Creepy! It's pitch black, almost like\Nthere is a hole in the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.62,0:13:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's scary how it feels like it could absorb you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and get away!\NGet as far away as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Go through the forest!\NRun all the way to the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Darkness is gravity!\NIt has the power to pull everything in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even a ray of light can\Nescape from its infinite gravity!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're up against me...\Nand I'm still untouched.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going after you just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stay there and\Nenjoy the view of the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:14:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Black Hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The ground is devouring the town!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark gravity uses its limitless power\Nto condense objects and crush them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a nightmare? Our village is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I'll show you what\Nhappened to the missing village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.02,0:15:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold the shambled mess it has become!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:15:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Liberation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Our village... has been reduced to rubble...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now do you get it, Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the power I've obtained!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Firefly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Fiery Doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot, hot, hot, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That burns!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,--I fully understand how great\Nthe power of darkness is.\N--Hot, hot, hot, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.21,0:17:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But here's what puzzles me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,--If it's a Logia, these attacks\Nshould go right through you.\N--Dang, this is hot! Hot, hot, hot, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you:\NDarkness draws everything in,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,including bullets, swords,\Npunches, fire, and lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike the rest of you, I don't get the\Noption of letting stuff pass through me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My body feels far worse pain than the\Naverage person in every way possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But in exchange for accepting that risk,\Nthere is one other thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...that I am able to absorb.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Vortex!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,To be exact, dark gravity has the ability
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to draw in a Devil Fruit\Npower holder's physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Gravity?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.82,0:18:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Have you figured it out, Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet it's been a while since someone's\Nlanded a punch on you, eh, Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that you got it when I grabbed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Another thing that my darkness drags in is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...Devil Fruit powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That means that while I'm touching them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.75,0:19:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Devil Fruit power holders\Ncan't use any of their powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.46,0:19:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Logia, Zoan, and Paramecia!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Against a world of Devil Fruit power holders\Nwho are overconfident in their abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've obtained a means of attack\Nthat cannot be defended against!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just can't let you catch me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I already proved that you can't\Nescape from my dark gravity!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Vortex!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Elmo's Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.78,0:19:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! The fire lances...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He messed up some vertebrae!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,His new power is a pain...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Cross Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Banana Rock...! It's collapsing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? They can't be humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget the village! What is going\Nto happen... to our whole island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I had assumed that Devil Fruit power holders\Nwere so preoccupied with their powers
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that they would be pushovers\Nonce they lost them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.27,0:20:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But I should have expected one\Nof Whitebeard's commanders
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,to be a fearsome fighter\Nin basic combat as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, today brings us\Nto another crossroad of fates.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.06,0:21:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is rendered\Npowerless before darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Even someone as powerful as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But this makes me want\Nyour power all the more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace, join my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I yield to power, there's no\Npoint in being born a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.46,0:21:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never leave anything to\Nbe regretted later in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand, stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.30,0:22:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How long can you live like that in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pity, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Die in darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.93,0:22:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Flame Commandment...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.07,0:22:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Flame Emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun or the darkness--\Nthere'll be only one winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.92,0:22:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna make Whitebeard the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.37,0:23:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The "Decisive Battle of Banaro Island"\Nin the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The fight between these two pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...will be described as the trigger for a\Nmassive incident that is soon to take place.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.56,0:23:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're hitting the sea of adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Head straight for Fishman Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.81,0:23:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no! With the New World nearby,\Nwe should exercise caution!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.44,0:23:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sanji! There's a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.03,0:23:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's missing both a sail and an ensign.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.69,0:23:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sailing full-speed\Ntoward trouble already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.16,0:23:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.49,0:23:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Mysterious Band of Pirates!\NSunny and the Dangerous Trap"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.20,0:23:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
